<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>qīng chén de gē shēng 迦南1350</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 qīng chén de gē shēng xiàng líng shēng chuán lái la la la la xiàng líng shēng chuán lái
 wǒ men de jìng bài xiàng tāo shēng pēng pài la la la la xiàng tāo shēng pēng pài
 qīng chén de qí dǎo xiàng zhōng shēng piāo lái la la la la xiàng zhōng shēng piāo lái
 tiān wèi wǒ men dǎ kāi zhǔ yé sū wǒ men xiàng nǐ jìng bài
 shù shuō nǐ yǒng héng zhī ài wǒ men rú tóng zhàn zài míng liàng de bō lí hǎi
 gē shēng bù duàn zhǔ yǒng yǔ tóng zài</lyrics>
<hymn_number>1350</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>